</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Louis Perea, a Colombian defender, said the team had seen the United States' 
tie with Switzerland, but did not immediately see any real likelihood that the 
U.S. style -- similar to the Romanians in its emphasis on deep defense -- would 
cause the Colombians to make major changes in Wednesday's game at the Rose 
Bowl. 
