<HEADLINE>
<P>
BASEBALL DAILY REPORT; AROUND THE MAJORS; SEGUI PLACED ON DISABLED LIST BY METS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
