<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSMAKERS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 C.L. Roy Nesbitt has joined the Southern California Production Group in Costa 
Mesa as an independent film and video producer. He previously worked as 
assistant director at Warner Bros. to film director Roland Joffe and 
