<DOCNO> LA062194-0117 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 053321 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 21, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura East Edition 
</P>
