 Television coverage of Monday's U.S. Open playoff was confusing. ABC had 
announced Sunday that coverage would run from 7-9:30 a.m. on ESPN and from 9:30 
to conclusion on ABC.But Monday, ABC decided not to pick up coverage until 11. 
