<P>
Postscript 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA062194-0317 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 053523 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 21, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition Correction Appended 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
World Report; Page 6; Column 1; World Report 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
